					<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/tl333s" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1304786); return false;"  ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1304786&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610183063" alt="TL333s" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1304786)"/></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/tl333s" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1304786); return false;" >TL333s</a></span> <span class="odate time_1358728438 format_%25e%20%25b%20%25Y%2C%20%25H%3A%25M%7Cagohover">21 Jan 2013 00:33</span>
														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-1690987">
									

<p>My upvote has been given highly grudgingly. My aversion to RPF (real-person fanfiction) and my lack of knowing who anyone on TGWTG is besides the Nostalgia Critic is warring with the fact that this is really hilarious and at least nails the reviewing style of internet nerds. Also &quot;What? What? What? What?&quot; was probably the best part.</p>
<p>I guess I should end with an admonition to be ashamed of yourself, but I just can't put my heart into it.</p>

